@startuml

[*] --> AddNewGoods

state "Add New Goods" as AddNewGoods
state "Update Price" as UpdatePrice
state "Remove Goods" as RemoveGoods
state "Identify Expired Goods" as IdentifyExpiredGoods
state "Place Order" as PlaceOrder
state "Generate Invoice" as GenerateInvoice
state "Search Items" as SearchItems
state "Calculate Discount and Tax" as CalculateDiscountTax
state "Generate Receipt" as GenerateReceipt
state "Replace Item or Cancel Receipt" as ReplaceItemCancelReceipt
state "Record Customer Requests" as RecordCustomerRequests
state "View Summary Report" as ViewSummaryReport

AddNewGoods --> UpdatePrice : update price of existing items
UpdatePrice --> RemoveGoods : remove goods from inventory
RemoveGoods --> IdentifyExpiredGoods : identify expired goods and notify user
IdentifyExpiredGoods --> PlaceOrder : place order for additional goods when required
PlaceOrder --> GenerateInvoice : generate invoice once order is placed
GenerateInvoice --> SearchItems : search for items available in the inventory and select them for purchase
SearchItems --> CalculateDiscountTax : calculate applicable discount and tax based on selected items
CalculateDiscountTax --> GenerateReceipt : generate receipt after purchase
GenerateReceipt --> ReplaceItemCancelReceipt : replace item or cancel receipt during billing process if needed
ReplaceItemCancelReceipt --> RecordCustomerRequests : record customer requests for items that may not be currently available
RecordCustomerRequests --> ViewSummaryReport : view summary report of all transactions carried out in the system at any point

[*] --> AddNewGoods

@enduml
